note over browser:
User click on the text box
type in note
press submit
end note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa
note over browser:
From data: {content: "this is an note", date: "2019-08-21"}
end note

server->browser: Code 201 {message: "this is an note"}

note over browser:
the application then redraw the page and
append the latest note at the bottom of the list
above the text box
end note
